From Bill Meyers Subject Re The Ballad of David Koresh In article C patricia anne withered writes The Ballad of David At Concord and at Waco the tyrant's minions Though they all died in the fire Koresh's people have Good The Waco finale was on April Patriot's On that day years earlier the militias of Concord and other nearby towns repelled a gun control raid by the then current Colonial government